replyContent:
An upfront apology for this issue, this is a bug.

This was previously noted and patched, however, it seems that we mistook the nature of the problem, and it wasn't fixed at all for several users.

A new patch is currently in the works, and should rollout (hopefully) between today and tomorrow.

Update: The issue has been fixed :)

content: The unavoidable google play service login that you can't pass ruins the game for me.
replyContent:
Hi, we're very sorry you are having issues with the Google Play sign in process, it was supposed to be an issue that was previously fixed, but due to a misjudgment over what the issue was, it was never successfully patched.

Do expect a fix soon.

Update: This issue has been fixed :)
